thread.title: BRIEF-Sun Hydraulics Sees 2017 Preliminary GAAP Net Income Per Diluted Share $1.10 - $1.14

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Sun Hydraulics Sees 2017 Preliminary GAAP Net Income Per Diluted Share $1.10 - $1.14
text:
Jan 29 (Reuters) - Sun Hydraulics Corp:
* SUN HYDRAULICS ANNOUNCES PRELIMINARY 2017 RESULTS * SUN HYDRAULICS CORP - SEES 2017 PRELIMINARY ESTIMATES OF CONSOLIDATED REVENUE BETWEEN $341.5 MILLION AND $343.5 MILLION
* SUN HYDRAULICS CORP - SEES 2017 PRELIMINARY ESTIMATES OF CAPITAL EXPENDITURES BETWEEN $22.1 MILLION AND $22.3 MILLION
* SUN HYDRAULICS CORP - SEES 2017 PRELIMINARY GAAP NET INCOME PER DILUTED SHARE $1.10 - 1.14
* SUN HYDRAULICS CORP - SEES 2017 PRELIMINARY NON-GAAP ADJUSTED NET INCOME PER DILUTED SHARE OF $1.54 - 1.58 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
